{"id":2750,"date":"2023-12-21T14:21:54","date_gmt":"2023-12-21T07:21:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/?p=2750"},"modified":"2023-12-21T14:21:54","modified_gmt":"2023-12-21T07:21:54","slug":"hoc-tap-qua-trai-nghiem-thuc-te-doanh-nghiep-cung-sinh-vien-khoa-kinh-te-luat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/hoc-tap-qua-trai-nghiem-thuc-te-doanh-nghiep-cung-sinh-vien-khoa-kinh-te-luat\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u1eccC T\u1eacP QUA TR\u1ea2I NGHI\u1ec6M TH\u1ef0C T\u1ebe DOANH NGHI\u1ec6P C\u00d9NG SINH VI\u00caN KHOA KINH T\u1ebe &#8211; LU\u1eacT"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sinh vi\u00ean Khoa Kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; Lu\u1eadt Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i C\u00f4ng ty EKF Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/span><\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp quan tr\u1ecdng, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u201cth\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc &#8211; th\u1ef1c l\u00e0m\u201d trong m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u201cNh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng &#8211; Doanh nghi\u1ec7p\u201d, \u0111\u1ec1 cao vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc \u0111i \u0111\u00f4i v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng Khoa c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c, li\u00ean k\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u doanh nghi\u1ec7p tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba b\u00e0n th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh l\u00e2n c\u1eadn, Khoa \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m, th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp, ki\u1ebfn t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u sinh vi\u00ean. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao l\u01b0u, chia s\u1ebb, h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u1edbi c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p, l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n nay.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_19674\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-19674\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-19674\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/IMG_0735-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-19674\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Sinh vi\u00ean Khoa Kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; Lu\u1eadt tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ty EKF Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y v\u00e0 tr\u00f2 Khoa Kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; Lu\u1eadt ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 C\u00f4ng ty c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n EKF Vi\u1ec7t Nam, m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng ty v\u1ec1 l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0 cung \u1ee9ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m trong x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft C\u00f4ng ty n\u00e0y thu\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1eb7ng Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00f9y, QTKD-K3 &#8211; C\u1ef1u sinh vi\u00ean Khoa Kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; Lu\u1eadt, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4. C\u1ef1u sinh vi\u00ean nh\u00e0 Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 sau khi t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb trong h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kinh nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00fd b\u00e1u c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u00e1ng cho c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Thadoer sau n\u00e0y h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 noi theo.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_19680\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-19680\" style=\"width: 2560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-19680\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/IMG_0873-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-19680\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Anh \u0110\u1eb7ng Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00f9y &#8211; C\u1ef1u sinh vi\u00ean Khoa Kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; Lu\u1eadt QTKD-K3, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 &#8211; Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c C\u00f4ng ty EKF Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Khoa &#8211; Tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ef1u sinh vi\u00ean c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m, l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn tin c\u1eady cho sinh vi\u00ean trong m\u1ed7i h\u1ecdc k\u1ef3 doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd gi\u1eefa Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ef1u sinh vi\u00ean, v\u00e0 m\u1ed1i li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa c\u1ef1u sinh vi\u00ean v\u00e0 sinh vi\u00ean. Nh\u1eefng anh ch\u1ecb \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 sau n\u00e0y, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng v\u1eefng m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-19678\" src=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/12\/IMG_0831-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">V\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi, ti\u1ebfp thu th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh, ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5, c\u01a1 c\u1ea5u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, kinh doanh v\u00e0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty, hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c h\u01a1n, hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc, x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngh\u1ec1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\">\u0110i nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c xu h\u01b0\u1edbng trong th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng lao \u0111\u1ed9ng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng tri\u1ec3n khai v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec trong su\u1ed1t m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n ngu\u1ed3n nh\u00e2n l\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eefng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, v\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng tay ngh\u1ec1, v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c sau t\u1ed1t nghi\u1ec7p, h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Roboto;\"><strong>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>\u0110\u1ecba ch\u1ec9: Km15, Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ed9 32, Kim Chung, Ho\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Hotline: 0934 07 8668 \u2013 0243 386 1601<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Website: <\/i><\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/\"><b><i>https:\/\/thanhdo.edu.vn\/<\/i><\/b><\/a><b><i>\u00a0<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Roboto; font-size: 12pt;\"><b><i>Fanpage: <\/i><\/b><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo\"><b><i>https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/truongdaihocthanhdo<\/i><\/b><\/a><\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Sinh vi\u00ean Khoa Kinh t\u1ebf &#8211; Lu\u1eadt Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc Th\u00e0nh \u0110\u00f4 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i C\u00f4ng ty EKF Vi\u1ec7t Nam Th\u1ef1c t\u1eadp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp quan tr\u1ecdng, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u201cth\u1ef1c h\u1ecdc &#8211; th\u1ef1c l\u00e0m\u201d trong m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u201cNh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng &#8211; Doanh nghi\u1ec7p\u201d, \u0111\u1ec1 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":9,"featured_media":2753,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[36],"tags":[109,110,123,42],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2750"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/9"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2750"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2750\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2754,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2750\/revisions\/2754"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2753"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2750"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2750"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/tuyensinh.thanhdo.edu.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2750"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}